title: Music Generations 20's
description: Give your project the special madness of the 20’s!
longDescription:
PRODUCED BY TAO & SOUND (Custom audio)


Music playlist


Music Generations 20’s is a unique music pack, made for game developers who need twenties-like realistic music loops for their videogames or for those devs who wish to enhance their games or apps with high quality charleston, fox-trot, big band jazz and ragtime themes.


These loops are suitable for sandbox, platformer, chase, runner or puzzle gameplay, in-game radio stations, main menus, credits scene, story scenes, cinematics or elegant background music for apps. It is, of course, perfect for MAFIA games.


Music Generations 20’s contains 8 original high quality music tracks with 8 old radio FX versions and 15 additional background music files (e.g. bass and drums only or melody only) carefuly chosen to offer more versatility for the different scenes of your game.


These 31 sound files are loopable (seamless). All main themes are above 1 minute lenght.


Questions? Please write us at contact@taoandsound.com , and we'll get back to you right away!
